Спеціально пишу українською, щоб сказати, що вас знають і люблять в Україні. Можливо не така велика кількість  фанатів, як в інших країнах. Хлопці,  ви неймовірні. Я так вами захоплююсь, вашим талантом. Ви всі такі різні, але водночас і доповнюєте один одного. Дуже дякую за те, що даруєте щасливі миті життя.
_____________________________________________________________________
I am writing in Ukrainian to say that you are known and loved in Ukraine. Maybe not as many fans as in other countries. You guys are incredible. I admire you so much, your talent. You are all so different, but at the same time you complement each other. Thank you so much for giving us happy moments of life.

美しい。8人それぞれの声が（顔も！！！！！）本当に美しい。消えてしまいそうな儚さと力強さが共存している。

バンチャン殿の安定感と息を呑むほどの魅力…

そしてそして！！！！！！私の！！！！！！チャンビンッッッッッッッッ！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！水面のようなビブラートの上で寝てもよろしい？？？？？？？？？？？？？？

author: @Kot-2405
text: Ну насчет сумасшедшего вокала, я конечно же поспорила бы (только тапками меня не закидайте, ведь любой профи это подтвердит).  Он далек, этот вокал,  на миллионы км от этого. НО!!!!! ( тут вся моя любовь к ребятам). Мальчики подобраны идеально, голосовые партии распределены великолепно тембрально настолько, насколько это возможно для не поющей, но очень музыкальной Корее. Композиторы в Корее- ЭТО РЕСПЕКТ, таких ОСТОВ нет нигде, как в Корее и Китае. Отдельный респект- хореографы!!!! Так технически красиво соединить музыку и танцы!!!! Ну и конечно же сами мальчики: великолепны, молоды, талантливы и почти все красивы. В части танцев вопросов нет. У всех все пластически, синхронно и технически точно. Молодость она такая. Ну и последнее, музыкальный выбор того, что они поют. Комбинация  музыкальных стилей и шикарные аранжировки, также шикарны, как собственно и танцы, коим я обозначаю мое уважение к хореографу!!!!. В  общем, ЗАЧЕТНО и удивительно профессионально все это выглядит, как шикарный и готовый продукт. Есть от чего сходить с ума. Ну и на последок скажу, что BTS, такого восприятия  удивления и восхищения на меня не произвел. Я считаю, что  группа STRAY KIDS, намного качественней, как БЭХА, вне времени и пространства,  дороже, шикарнее, красивее и самое главное, харизматичнее. Желаю мальчикам всего самого удивительного и каждому , птицу счастья в подарок.

author: @bread-us2cy
text:
Jesus loves you all so much He died on the cross for you in your place! Since we deserve eternal death because we are human and we sin, we automatically fall short of God’s glory. God understood this, and became human in the form of Jesus. Jesus taught us not to hate, but to love everyone. He is God, and washed the feet of others to teach us to care for one another. Not to judge. 

So, what is sin? Sin is going against God’s will. After we sin once, we should be dead and separated from God. BUT. JESUS DIED FOR US ON THE CROSS. He picked up His cross and carried it and only thought of you. He felt pain, loneliness, sadness, anxiety, happiness, love, joy, and temptation. God became human and experienced everything humans experience. He understands you. 

Think you’re too unclean or sinful for Him? Think about this: do you go to a bath already clean? No, you go to a bath to get clean. When you sin, go to God first. He is bigger than any of our sins combined. He made the universe and heaven! He cares for you. 

Things get tough and sometimes you may question if God is even there. But He is. Think of this: when you first ride your bike without training wheels, you will fall and scrape your knees. It’s not easy, but you learn, and become better and better as you practice! God puts us through lessons! He is there every step of the way, so we don’t need to be afraid of anything! He builds us. Once you give your surrender to Him, let Him guide you. 

How can you surrender to God? Tell God right now “God, I believe what Jesus did for me. I want to start new with You. I accept You into my life. Forgive me Lord, You are my salvation.” (It doesn’t need to be word for word, just be genuine, and He can help you with being genuine as well). Sometimes, you won’t know what to do or say. And that’s okay, you’re not perfect. But God is!! Trust in His forgiveness. You are made right with God through faith in Him and what He can do. A lot can happen in a week. Jesus has been through it. One day, everyone was shouting “Hosanna: Blessed is the King of Israel that cometh in the name of the Lord.” (John 12:13) A few days later, those same people praising Him were yelling “Crucify Him!” But, He rose from the dead! He conquered death, and now sits at the right Hand of God the Father Almighty. You are made new in the Holy Spirit Who is also the same One God, in Spirit form. The Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit are One God combined. They are all equally God. The Holy Spirit will remind you of God’s word. God’s voice is often thought of as loud, scary, or thunderous. No, God’s voice is quiet, gentle, and knows exactly what to say in your mind. He can also speak through other people and things, but it must relate back to His word . If it doesn’t, it’s not from God. If it rushes you, makes you anxious, or pressures you, it’s not God, it’s the enemy trying to impersonate God. But don’t worry! God is with you on your side ready to be your shield always. He is power is bigger than anything, and any evil. You can read God’s word on Bible.com! His presence is lovely, and relaxing. He wants a relationship with you now!
“Now this is eternal life: that they know You the true God and Jesus Christ, whom You have sent.” (John 17:3). It’s not about if you’re  just a good person. It’s about knowing God and having faith in Him. When you have faith in God, He will guide your works to glorify Him and to help you to become the best version of you. Start new with God today. You’re ready to. Spread this message! ❤

author: @Okulöncesiöğretmeni95
text:
진짜 완벽해. 이번에도 훌륭한 일을 해냈다.  스키즈, 대한민국의 자랑앴어.  내 마음의 왕자들 (특히 리노 ♡) 

그나저나 저는 터키 STAY이자 유치원 교사이기도 해 (아이엔의 꿈 😇..정인아 항상 일 잘해요.) 우리의 경력은 SKZ와 동시에 시작됐는데 매우 소중해요 나에게.  왜냐하면 스키즈 데뷔했을 때 나는 데뷔 1년차였으니까요.  당신처럼 나도 인턴이었고, 인턴 생활이 고통스럽고 힘들었다고 말할 수 있다. 사실 당신이 제게 영감을 주는 게 정말 좋아요.  나는 스키즈 와 함께 점점 더 강해지고 있다.  아 그나저나 내가 찬보다 2살 많으니까 찬이는 이제 안 늙었구나..😂

스트레이키즈는 항상 좋은 것 같아요.  스키즈 가 나에게 천사이고, 나에게 힘을 주고, 나에게 영감을 주고, 모든 일에서 나를 행복하게 해주는 사람들로 구성되어 있습니다. ❤️

author: @kuju2315
text:
Stray kids is a legendary group with the most diverse discography. Stray kids are huge in the music industry. They are top producers . Only groups in k-pop that are  self made ( chan picked the members) and self produced groups .
From the newest  album 5 star,Rock Star and lose my breath,hall of frame ,FNF, item,leave ,cover me, the sound, super bowl, Youtiful,blind spot,time out and obviously S-Class, lalalala etc . 

Soft song - never ending, winter fall,4419, spread my wings, 24 to 25, OH, leventer, blue print, Ex, red light, hoodie season,for you , lonely st, silent cry,charmer, on track,time out, novel , there, the view your eyes,  blue print, star lost etc. 

Brilliant song - venom, freeze, grrr, mirror, miroh, maze of memories, chronosaurus, 3racha  side effect ,top, 3racha , slump,god's menu, thunderous, TA, cheese,muddy water, the sound, slump,top etc.

Old gems - hellevator, district 9, my pace, awkward silence,19, road not taken,boxer, question,M.I.A,get cool,I am you , yayaya, grow up , stop, booster, astronaut, maze of memories,side effects, mixtape 1,2,3,4, entrance, hero's soup,my side etc.
From start to now they give so many beautiful songs.

People need to watch the intro of each album to know how they come up with the idea and concept and meaning behind the song and all details and work they do on every song.

Stray kids are known for the quality of music and dedication for music.They are very creative and unique and versatile.  Stray kids is inspiring to so many people. Their music is something connected with  people .They give motivation, inspiration  to express yourself it's ok to be unique You are beautiful the way you are. stray kids discography is very diverse with life philosophy. 
I describe stray kids music is
"EXPRESSION OF LIFE"
EXPRESSION OF PEOPLE" "EXPRESSION OF EMOTIONS"
 Lyrics are beautifully expressed with  so many meanings . 
They have a diverse discography. I love the  intellect, cleverness and creativity in songs. They have a very organic,fresh and  unique sound. They didn't limited themself and explore the new side of music. You see so many new, refreshing and experimental sounds in their music. They explore different genres and express different emotions and touch so many important subjects like social pressure , anxiety, mental health, loneliness, depression insomnia etc. 
They break many stereotypes in music. The more you listen to them the more you admire and become addicted to them and respect them more as artists. The music they made is connected with people with beautiful messages , inspiration and motivation . ❤❤❤

author: @kuju2315
text:
Stray kids They are definitely  dominating  the k-pop. They are huge in  the music industry. They are top producers. They are legends with huge discography.They are making history in billboards continuously  4 time #1in 200, most pre order in k-pop history, top most sales, they are most awarded in 4th gen( best group , best performance group, album of the year, most popular group, group of the year etc.) first group that make many records, first and only one to perform  in many events, shows and festivals, first in k-pop in history to k-pop group attend the metgala. And many more achivement.

They are the  most successful group we have . 
Stray kids have all quality which make them legends of k-pop . Plus also make apart  from other generation of group like Big Bang, exo, Bts, snsd, black pink, twice and other many groups is -
 
•  Self- made - They are the First fully self made group in k-pop. Chan picked all group members,  they made the name,concept, and logo.
 On the other hand other groups are made by the company.

• Self- produce - Stray kids is a self produced group from the start of their discography made by themselves. They are the ones to make  beats, melody, write lyrics, compose songs,record the song,and edit, arrange the song etc. other groups become successful thanks to other producers, composers, and lyricists. 

•  Innovation - They step out  from stereotypes of music and make new organic , fresh creative,innovative music that is lacking  in other groups, other groups play safe to please the people and make repetitive songs. 

• Artistic value -stray kid's half of group is doing dance , producing, composing, writing songs before they debut ( 3racha and Lee know backup dancer) and with skz player and skz record they always give music to the world because they love what they do. On the other hand see Many other idols are coming to industry for stardom,frame and money they didn't care about music and doing other things like modeling, acting,advertising etc forgetting about their main job singing and creating music.

•Genuine Music - stray kids give depth and meaning to music,  categories such as " " EXPRESSION OF EMOTION'S" EXPRESSION OF LIFE"
"EXPRESSION OF PEOPLE'S" 
 Others want popularity from music.

• Brilliant producers -  all members are producer's 3racha is a regular member of KOMCA ,Bangchan has the most song credits  -181,
 changbin -152, Han-148 and  all other members have above 20 songs credits. Didn't see any groups with all producer members or with so many song credits.

• large spectrum - they make songs about many different topics like from hallevator to rock star.  astronaut, circus, school life, question, mirror, insomnia, side effects, Airoplane ,voice,my pace, who etc they have a large spectrum of songs. 

• Genres  - they cover genres from rock , EDM, soft, Hip hop, ballad , electro, R and B , experimental music ,folk (thunderous ),heavy metal etc have like 40- 50+ gener. They have a huge discography. Didn't see this many genres in other groups. 

•  Great Creator - stray kids are the creator and  presenter of the song . That is very unique in k-pop.They put every emotion in every song. Because they know the depth of the song. Didn't feel emotion in other groups because they are just the presenter of  song . 

•  Genius Lyricists - they are  very  clever,creative and unique, with many Wordplay, 3-4 different meanings in lyrics. That is very rare in the k-pop industry. Hellevator, noeasy, oddinary, chronosaurus, Rock is the example of this. 

•Social awareness - stray kids have the courage to bring up topics that are taboo to talk but they are important topics of youths like depression, loneliness, insomnia, phobia, side effects social pressure, etc that topics come from them is mesmerizing. And i respect them to brave enough bring this topic.

•social  work- stray kids is a one of the group they help people from donation to UNICEF,and other organisations,or with  volunteer work or  in EDM project or by doing social work,or with meaningful lyrics or to communicate with people to give advice to never give up, how deal with depression or they say they are always here to listen. They always help people one or other ways. 

•Realistic  - stray kids  make very realistic songs, they are relatable to the people many groups promote fantasy and imaginary concepts far from reality.

• Talents - they are very talented rappers, singers and dancers. All members are  singers and dancers, rappers, composers,producers,song writers and many more they have unique voice strength. This many Talents are so rare in k-pop . 

•Concepts - stray kid's image is like normal human beings they achieve everything by hard work which is why people feel more related  to them. In k-pop others  groups promote idol image like god , that normal human is unreachable to them. 

• connection- Stray kids is one of the group that has deep connection with people  to the point, like they are telling our story. Their music is described as "life philosophy" . Their music comes from experience. 
 with another group you don't feel that deep connected with them . 

•Youth inspiration -  Their journey is very inspiring.  In their journey people see the hard work,how to overcome the struggle, to never give up, love others, be positive. They come this far because of hardwork and dedication. They are inspiring so many peoples. Many people look up to them.

They are the most  impactful group in the  k-pop music industry.stray kid's  music will be dominating in the music industry for many  decades. Stray kids came from zero to top by themselves.They are working hard and achieving the success they deserve. people love about  Stray kids music that you not only listen to k-pop sound in their music but they give  something new, fresh, innovative and experimental  to the music industry with their songs.

 Lyrics are beautifully expressed with  so many meanings .  love the  intellect, cleverness and creativity in songs. They have a very organic,fresh and unique sound. They didn't limited themself and explore the new side of music.
They break many stereotypes in music. They explore so many genres and express different emotions. More you listen to them the more you admire and become addicted to them and respect them more as artists. The music they make is connected with people with beautiful messages, inspiration  and motivation . ❤❤❤

O quanto eu amo esse vídeo não está escrito! Stray Kids servindo vocais e jogando na cara daqueles que dizem que eles não tem talento nenhum! Eu como Stay nunca estive tão feliz!!! Vocês realmente me fizeram lose my breath! ♡

LEE KNOW, amo que sua voz doce e angelical está sendo cada vez mais usada nas músicas!

CHANGBIN, o que foi esse vocal!!! Ninguém estava preparado e você veio e assolou com a gente!!!

HYUNJIN, é tão bom te ouvir cantando ao vivo. Obrigada!

HAN, meu rockstar, você nunca me decepciona! Não é a toa que é o meu UTT!

FÉLIX, sua voz grave sempre acalentando o coração de Stay!

SEUNGMIN, O CANTOR QUE VOCÊ É! ME SINTO REALMENTE PRIVILEGIADA EM OUVIR CADA LINHA QUE VOCÊ CANTA!!!

IN, fico feliz em ver seus vocais melhorando a cada dia. Estarei sempre em dívida com você!

YOU MAKE STRAY KIDS STAY ♡

author: @biancaa_felix
text: jype messed up big time, this wasn’t a good career move. they were not able to surpass their previous achievements despite the constant promotions. LA4 got little to no promo, but they achieved that ranking on their own, with their own effort. LMB had triple the promotions and didn’t really do much for them. stays insisted that skz needed this irrelevant man for their western debut, despite them having been famous internationally for quite some time now. but no one here even likes him, and he did them no favors. and them proceeding to post multiple selfies w him shows that they don’t empathize with their fans critique at all, and they support a rape apologist and zionist. many debut stays have been uncomfortable and left the fandom because of this. was all of this worth it? long time genuine fans of stray kids are parting ways with them, the ones that didn’t care about charts, the ones who cared about skz and their music. stray kids has lost something more valuable than a #90 on the billboard charts and it’ll never come back. i say this to show how truly embarrassing of a move this was on jype’s part. this boycott was done for the people of palestine, their lives are more important than charts. you can tell that most of stray kids current fanbase is chart obsessed and doesn’t care that this goes against skz values. they don’t care about human lives, they are all apathetic towards the effect that zionism has had on the world and the ongoing genocide in palestine. i don’t think the fanbase can ever move on from this, and its possibly that skz will lose more of their genuine, long time fans for this. i made this comment to share my opinion and show my disappointment in them, which i am allowed to do.

text:
Seungmin is the real, most beautiful and 
most precious diamond that this world did 
not deserve. It is a pity for those people who completely forgot those who do not know at 
all and do not even try to find out: Chan chose Seungmin not only because he is smart and well-mannered, but first of all because that he is versatile, versatile and incredibly talented. The natural pattern "the most precious diamonds and the brightest stars are hidden from human eyes" now I began to understand this as never before.

author: @liza_pet
text:
For so many years in K-POP, I haven't seen 
any beautiful and talented idols, but I can't 
even explain Seungmin in words. Truly, an angel whose beauty is created by heaven and sparkles brighter than the stars, eclipsing everything around, a voice as clear as crystal, gentle as a cloud and deeper than the ocean, which is only worth hearing and you are completely powerless before it. His voice is salvation and damnation at the same time, it is like a balm for the soul and warms your heart like the dearest person at the same time piercing your soul through, tearing apart, touching the farthest corners of your 
heart, leaving you "the way you are."

author: @irisheyes9912
text: I absolutely love this song & a few words stuck out, like "lungs"  and "lose my breath" .  I'm really sick & found out I have pneumonia in both lungs and the Dr said the X-rays show a neoplasm nodule in my lung (I don't remember which one).  I have to get more X-rays done in 3-4 weeks to get a clearer image once the pneumonia starts to clear up.  From there they will biopsy it & go from there.  I love singing, & the thought of not singing again is so depressing.  I've had cancer before, it runs in my family on both sides, my dad has it again for the 2nd time.  I'm sorry, I'm just still in shock, I just found out about my diagnosis earlier today.

text: I’m absolutely in love with this song! Lee Know shines throughout the whole song, despite the song being in English. Bang Chan and Seungmin singing together is absolutely beautiful (they need a song together!). Actually, Seungmin throughout the whole song sounds beautiful and shows how much he’s improved. Changbin definitely needs to sing in more songs because his singing is wonderful! It shows another side of him that he should show more often. Felix and Hyunjin’s rapping gives the song a cool edge and brings their classic “stray kids” sound to the song. And I.N and Han had amazing voices as they always do. Our boys did amazing ❤️

author: @liza_pet
text: Seungmin's vocals and visual are just something unthinkable and incomprehensible. I can't take my eyes off him from the first second of the first day, but now I don't even have words to describe how much he has changed and grown, and in all meaningful ways. Seungmini is not only divinely beautiful, he literally shines brighter than the stars, eclipsing absolutely everything and everything. And his unique voice conquered my heart irrevocably and definitively from the first note, but with what power and strength it sounds now, what professional level has it reached. If I thought so before, now I am absolutely sure that Seungmin is not just ready, but will shine even brighter with his solo album.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Seungmin always puts so many feelings 
and emotions into absolutely every song, in absolutely every part and note. A voice that just needs to be heard as tears flow like a stream and my heart is pounding so fast jumping out of my chest and I can't do anything about it at all. He was perfectly in control of his voice from the very beginning and how much he has grown during this time, what a high professional level he has reached and nevertheless continues to improve and continues to work. Seungmin is the real treasure not only of STRAY KIDS, not only of the K-POP industry, but of the entire music world. In so many years in the K-POP industry, I have never met such an idol as Seungmin, in fact, I shouldn't have because he really is the only one.

author: @liza_pet
text:
I've always had and will have a little of Seungmin, I can't stop being amazed by him in this song, video and album as a whole. He has changed 
so much, matured and grew up at a professional level, although very little time has passed since the S-CLASS comeback and it is impossible to recognize Seungmin. Even his look has become completely different, more confident, and his eyes sparkle even brighter, as well as the visual of Seungmini is unrealistically beautiful, but what he is now cannot be described in any words, that's honestly I can't. He perfectly owns his voice amazing high notes angelic timbre and it has always been so only now his vocals have truly opened up with new power and force thundering all over the world. I just love the way he dances, his style of movement is so natural, while absolutely always clear and clean, it's really given to him, and with this choreography he blew up and burned everything around such a colossal return. I'm looking forward to Seungmin's solo album more than anything.

author: @liza_pet
text:
No record, no disc will transfer all the beauty, depth, strength and power of Seungmin's voice. The most precious diamonds and the brightest stars are hidden from human eyes, and it's not for nothing that when I met Seungmin, 
I understand this like never before.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Literally every album every song and every performance of Seungmin's voice is a discovery, it never ceases to amaze, and to such an extent that you lose not only the power of speech but also your pulse. A voice that I want to listen to endlessly and how much more potential there 
is in it, I'm even afraid to imagine. I will never 
stop admiring Seungmin and praying for his 
solo album.

Outro destaque que ta incrível sao as partes do Leeknow, meus amores arrasando demais como sempre! Como é bom ser Stay e cada dia poder ter mais orgulho ainda de ser fã dos melhores, da pra ver o quanto trabalharam e trabalham duro! Amo muito ❤

author: @puzzledmind
text:
They all sound so good in this live version 😍 8 vocalists! Seungmin’s high notes and his aldibs are so divine! Lee Know sang so beautifully too, I can’t get enough of his voice. Chan and Han sounded so natural, I love them singing in English. Felix and Hyunjin slayed the 2nd verse - better than the studio version imo. I.N worries because he thought Seungmin was really good and he was pressured because his line was after Seungmin’s… I.N did a very good job, the transition was smooth. And finally, Changbin… the rapper Changbin turned into vocal Changbin. I wish he could sing more in the future ❤️

Overall, I am just so proud of this song especially this version. Please do more live versions of your future songs too 🥹 great job, SKZ!

text:
I don't think I'll ever get over Changbin's sound duality when singing vs rapping ever but Seungmin's adlibs are so addicting too 😭💕 I love the outro of this song so much aaaaaaaaaaa

Edit: I didn't expect this comment to blow up but all of them did very well! There's just very few clips of Changbin singing out there and I've always loved how he could pull off both so well but so differently too, which makes those few seconds just hit me different 🥹
I only mentioned Seungmin's adlib coz I thought he was the one doing adlibs since the last chorus until the end while Chan is the one mainly singing the lyrics 😅 But it was actually the other way around in post-chorus sorry asdfghjk

Needless to say, despite their "original positions", OT8 have amazing vocals and this song showcased them!
